==English==
===Etymology===
An abbreviation of ‘brothel-house’, ultimately from Old English [[breoþan|brēoþan]] ‘degrade, deteriorate’.

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun|brothel|brothels}}

# A house of [[prostitution]]

